```

**Critical trust boundary issues identified:**
1. Admin panel reads ALL users via **client-side Firestore** (`getDocs(collection(db, "users"))`) — bypasses admin auth middleware
2. Admin panel writes subscription upgrades via **client-side Firestore** (`updateDoc`) — bypasses protected field rules
3. `usePremium` hook runs on client — all feature gating is client-side enforced only
4. Rate limiter is **in-memory** on serverless (resets on cold start) — not persistent

