## Admin Flow

The admin panel at `/admin` is a **client-side page** with these powers:

| Capability | Implementation | Risk Level |
|-----------|---------------|------------|
| View ALL users | Client Firestore `getDocs` | 🔴 HIGH |
| Create promo accounts | Client Firebase Auth + Firestore | 🔴 HIGH |
| Grant Pro subscriptions | Client Firestore `updateDoc` | 🔴 CRITICAL |
| Generate referral links | Client Firestore `setDoc` to promo_codes | 🟡 MEDIUM |
| Sync Razorpay → Firestore | authenticatedFetch to admin API | 🟢 OK |

> [!CAUTION]
> **The admin panel performs MOST operations via client-side Firestore SDK, NOT the Admin SDK.** The only server-side admin operation is the Razorpay sync. The email check (`user.email !== ADMIN_EMAIL`) is purely frontend — Firestore rules don't restrict reading all users to admin.

