### Firestore Security Rules Summary

| Collection | Read | Write | Notes |
|-----------|------|-------|-------|
| `users/{uid}` | Own doc only | Own doc (create/update), can't touch `subscription`, `isPromo`, `maxTierPassed` | ✅ Well-protected |
| `results/{id}` | Own docs (by userId field) | Create only (immutable) | ✅ Good |
| `ai_chats/{id}` | Own docs (by userId field) | Create only | ✅ Good |
| `promo_codes/{code}` | Any authenticated user | Deny all | ✅ Good |
| `ai_usage/{date}` | Deny all | Deny all | ✅ Admin SDK only |
| `webhook_events/{id}` | Deny all | Deny all | ✅ Admin SDK only |
| `{everything else}` | Deny all | Deny all | ✅ Default deny |

