| **OpenAI API** | Single user exhausts 75k output tokens/day = ~$0.30/day on GPT-4o-mini. But if token budget check fails, unlimited tokens. | 💰💰💰 |
| **Razorpay check-user-status** | Iterates 1000 API calls (500 subs + 500 payments) per user check. 1000 users = 1M Razorpay API calls/day. | 💰💰 |
| **Firestore reads (Admin)** | Admin loads ALL user documents on every page load. At 10k users = 10k reads per admin visit. | 💰💰 |
| **Firestore reads (Auth)** | Every auth state change reads the user doc. Frequent tab switches = repeated reads. | 💰 |
| **Vercel Serverless** | Exam XML parsing reads multiple files per request (up to 10 chapters × ~20KB each). At scale, could hit memory limits. | 💰 |

